item.title: Someone got a economi resetter that reset all items from all players?
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“JvSwift, post:5, topic:303299”]just did a quick search of moparscape …

[quote author=marcbob link=topic=364243.msg2765147#msg2765147 date=1240761945]

Title Economy Reseter
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe” EconomyReset.class
java EconomyReset
pause[/quote]

just create a new text document paste that in it, change the jdk to your version and save as Economy Reset.bat… and make sure its saved as a java file and not a .txt…[/quote]

Except you forgot possibly the most important part…

Where is the class file?

Basically, all you have to do is make a loop that cycles through all the characters, and then a BufferedReader to read up until the item’s part of the char files begins, then you have two options. You can either wipe all of the items from every character, or you can choose which items you want deleted.
